                    ),
                  ),
                ],
              ),
            ),
            // Store List
            Expanded(
              child: filteredStores.isNotEmpty
                  ? ListView.builder(
                      padding: const EdgeInsets.all(16),
                      itemCount: filteredStores.length,
                      itemBuilder: (context, index) {
                        final store = filteredStores[index];
                        return GestureDetector(
